() Tj
T*
(Text uses:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- text_transformer when installed and available,) Tj
T*
(- the classical text bundle as fallback,) Tj
T*
(- small label-specific retuning for weaker text domains such as depression, loneliness, anxiety, substance abuse, sleep disorder, and stress.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The stronger labels are left mostly unchanged.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 6. Comorbidity Fusion) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The comorbidity head combines:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- classifier-chain ensemble probabilities,) Tj
T*
(- upstream modality consensus from text, audio, and image,) Tj
T*
(- calibration and pairwise lift metadata.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This helps the weakest bundle benefit more from stabilized upstream predictions instead of relying only on deeper chain tuning.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(## 7. Related Files) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
